c: 9
v: 19
t: "Nemhaka yei muchitora kupa mvura kuavo vanouya kuHajj neavo vanogadzira paAl-Masjid Al- Haraam (kuMakkah) sevakafanana neuyo anotenda kuna Allah uye muzuva rokupedzisira, uye anoshanda nesimba nekurwa munzira yaAllah? Havana kufanana pamberi paAllah. Uye Allah havaratidzi gwara avo vanotadza"